This roll bundles the PGI compilers.  To install, execute these instructions
on a Rocks development machine (e.g., a frontend), starting in this directory:

% make
% rocks add roll *.iso
% rocks enable roll pgi
% cd /export/rocks/install
% rocks create distro
% rocks run roll pgi | bash

In addition to the software itself, the roll installs PGI environment module
files in /opt/modulefiles/compilers/pgi.
